Seasonal Specials









																								
										Chicken Caesar Parmesan Crisp Sandwich																						


Grilled chicken breast, house made garlic aioli, Caesar dressing, parmesan cheese crisp, chopped romaine, sliced tomato on a grilled sourdough bun.



10.50 




																								
										Buffalo Chicken BLT Salad																						



Mixed greens, grilled chicken breast, grape tomatoes, cheddar and blue cheese, diced bacon, croutons, Buffalo Garlic sauce and tossed in Ranch dressing. 



10.95 

 




																								
										Fried Green Tomatillos																						
GF


Hand breaded pickled tomatillo slices lightly fried to perfection, served with your favorite signature sauce.



7.50 

 
 







