										Chili Mac																						



Cavatappi noodles, cheddar, Parmesan, Gouda, mozzarella, Turkey Black Bean Chili, jalapeños, guacamole, pico de gallo, cilantro.



9.95 

 
 







Burgers & Sandwiches





Burgers and sandwiches served with Hand-Cut Fries or Dave’s Sweet Potato Chips® and choice of dipping sauce. Upgrade to any premium (P) side for only 2.50.
All burgers available as a Bagger Bowl (no bun.) Beef/Turkey burgers offered in a petite patty size or a la carte for 1.00 less.



Specialty Burgers







																								
										Santa Fe Chipotle Turkey Burger																						
 


Two all-natural turkey patties, pepper jack, coleslaw, tomato, guacamole, Santa Fe Chipotle sauce, grilled nine grain wheat bun. 



BEER: Brown Ale or Pilsner													

WINE: Riesling or Semi-Sweet Red													



10.95 




																								
										Mushroom & Swiss Turkey Stack																						


Swiss cheese, house-made Garlic Aioli, sautéed mushrooms and two all-natural turkey patties on a grilled brioche bun. 



BEER: Lager													

WINE: Chardonnay													



9.50 

 




																								
										Asian Turkey Burger *																						


Two all-natural turkey patties, coleslaw, alfalfa sprouts, Asian Sesame sauce, crispy wontons, grilled sesame seed brioche bun.



BEER: Wheat													

WINE: Merlot or Sauvignon Blanc													



10.50 




																								
										Fiery Bleu Buffalo Turkey Burger																						



Two all-natural turkey patties, bleu cheese, coleslaw, tomato, Buffalo Garlic sauce, grilled sesame seed brioche bun.



BEER: IPA or Lager													

WINE: Riesling or White Zinfandel													



9.95 

 




																								
										Black Bean Veggie Burger																						



Chipotle black bean burger, lettuce, tomato, pickled tomatillos, pico de gallo, guacamole, Santa Fe Chipotle sauce, grilled nine grain bun. 



BEER: IPA													

WINE: Sauvignon Blanc													



10.95 




																								
										Blackened Mahi-Mahi Burger																						



Lettuce, tomato, pickled red onions, guacamole, black bean corn salsa, Santa Fe Chipotle sauce, grilled nine grain bun.



BEER: IPA or Light Lager													

WINE: Moscato													



12.50 

 
 


Prime-Rib Burgers
Made from a distinctive combination of perfectly seasoned sirloin, chuck and prime rib. Never frozen and locally sourced from 100% grain fed cattle with no fillers or preservatives.
Regular burgers are cooked pink or no pink, petite size cooked to no pink.







																								
										Train Wreck Burger®*																						



Cheddar, sunny side up egg, Hand-Cut Fries, caramelized onions, sautéed mushrooms, lettuce, Railhouse Thousand Island® sauce, grilled sesame brioche bun.



BEER: Brown Ale or Stout													

WINE: Malbec or Merlot													



12.50 




																								
										Bacon BBQ Burger																						


Applewood smoked bacon, cheddar, caramelized onions, lettuce, tomato, BBQ
sauce, grilled brioche bun. Try it with Chipotle BBQ sauce.



BEER: Brown Ale or Porter													

WINE: Malbec or Semi-Sweet Red													



11.50 

 




																								
										Caleb’s Crispy Cheese Bacon Burger*																						


Applewood smoked bacon, cheddar and Parmesan cheese crisp, tomato, lettuce, mayonnaise, grilled sesame seed brioche bun.



BEER: Pale Ale or Pilsner													

WINE: Cabernet or Merlot													



11.50 




																								
										Saucy Sicilian Pizza Burger® 


Artisan pepperoni, mozzarella, Parmesan, sautéed mushrooms, caramelized onions, fresh basil, marinara sauce, grilled pretzel bun.



BEER: Fruit/Wheat													

WINE: Cabernet or Zinfandel													



11.95 

 




																								
										Korean BBQ Burger																						


Korean BBQ beef, sunny side up egg, kimchi, lettuce, pickled red onions, alfalfa sprouts, Korean BBQ sauce, crispy wontons, grilled sesame seed brioche bun. 



BEER: IPA													

WINE: Red Blend													



12.50 




																								
										Mexicali Burger*																						



Pepper jack, refried beans, coleslaw, jalapeños, banana peppers, pickled tomatillos, guacamole, Santa Fe Chipotle sauce, grilled brioche bun. 



BEER: Amber													

WINE: Malbec													



11.50 

 




																								
										The Blues Burger® 



Bleu cheese crumbles, tomato, lettuce, Cajun spice, Santa Fe Chipotle sauce, grilled pretzel bun. 



BEER: IPA or Stout													

WINE: Malbec													



10.50 




																								
										Great American Cheeseburger																						


American cheese, lettuce, tomato, pickles, ketchup, mustard, mayonnaise, grilled sesame seed brioche bun.



BEER: Pale Ale or Pilsner													

WINE: Cabernet or Pinot Noir													



9.50 

 
 


Sandwiches







																								
