Terms and ConditionsBagger Bucks™ allows you to receive certain rewards, which may not be identified to you in advance. You must be at least 13 years of age to participate in Bagger Bucks™. Some activities may only be available to members who are at least 21 years of age. Number, type and frequency of rewards are based upon a number of factors, each subject to change, including without limitation, visits, volume and type of purchases at participating Bagger Dave’s, type and amount of personal information provided, and type and amount of participation in and/or interaction with Bagger Bucks™ activities. Activities to earn rewards do not count towards, and may not be combined with, activities described under other Programs. When earned, rewards will be identified on your User account page and may also be printed on your receipt. Rewards must be applied at time of visit. You are not obligated to accept or utilize any rewards. Rewards will be deemed forfeited if not used within allotted time frame. Rewards are subject to change or substitution without notice. Rewards may not be exchanged for cash, any cash equivalent or any other products, or combined with other discounts, coupons or Programs. A unique and valid email address may be required. Rewards may not be earned or redeemed if unexpected technical difficulties arise. Bagger Dave’s has no responsibility to retroactively apply rewards.








 

























