Bagger Dave's Burger Tavern Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















bagger dave's burger tavern inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Gaming, Lodging & Restaurants
Sub-Industry: Restaurants
Bagger Dave's Burger Tavern, Inc. owns and operates a chain of full-service casual restaurants and bars. The Company offers rib recipe and all-natural lean turkey burgers, hand-cut fries, beers, milk shakes, salads, and black bean turkey chili. Bagger Dave's Burger Tavern serves customers throughout the United States.




